Mithril.

1282
02:20:06.232 --> 02:20:08.814
You are full of surprises.
master Baggins.

1283
02:20:14.824 --> 02:20:16.780
To the bridge of khazad-dum!

1284
02:20:31.758 --> 02:20:33.339
Aragorn: This way!

1285
02:21:43.747 --> 02:21:46.739
What is this new devilry?

1286
02:22:02.849 --> 02:22:05.636
A balrog.

1287
02:22:05.935 --> 02:22:09.098
A demon of the ancient world.

1288
02:22:11.274 --> 02:22:13.731
This foe is beyond any of you.

1289
02:22:14.903 --> 02:22:16.439
Run!

1290
02:22:23.787 --> 02:22:25.277
Quickly!

1291
02:22:41.930 --> 02:22:43.170
(Sandalf.

