Steady.

1305
02:25:07.951 --> 02:25:09.111
Come on!

1306
02:25:09.369 --> 02:25:10.859
Now!

1307
02:25:28.096 --> 02:25:29.882
Over the bridge!

1308
02:25:30.139 --> 02:25:31.629
Fly!

1309
02:26:16.352 --> 02:26:18.343
You cannot pass!

1310
02:26:18.521 --> 02:26:20.182
(Gandalf!

1311
02:26:24.402 --> 02:26:29.271
I am a servant of the secret fire.
wielder of the flame of anor.

1312
02:26:30.283 --> 02:26:34.026
The dark fire will not avail you.
flame of ud[N!

